# Optional agent credentials — the practice loop itself needs NO secrets.
#
# In GitHub Codespaces, prefer Codespaces secrets over a local file: add these
# names at Settings → Codespaces → Secrets before creating the codespace.
# Locally, export them in your shell — the justfile deliberately does not
# auto-load dotenv files (`set dotenv-load := false`).
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=    # Claude Code as interviewer (alt: run `claude` and log in)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=       # OpenAI Codex as interviewer (alt: `codex login --device-auth`)
